<h1>Over 70 agencies in SPPD's network hold active ICE 287(g) agreements</h1>

<p>Cross-indexing the 602+ SPPD shared-network agencies against ICE's official 287(g) participant list (1,503 agencies) found <strong>{{ crossindex.total }} matches</strong>. These are agencies that both have SPPD camera access and hold an active ICE collaboration agreement.</p>

<h2>Verify this yourself</h2>

<h3>Step 1: Download the data</h3>

<p><a href="{{ "/outputs/sppd-287g-crossindex/crossindex_results.csv" | url }}" class="cta">Download crossindex_results.csv</a></p>

<p>Source files used in the cross-index:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="{{ "/data/derived/sppd-shared-networks/sppd-shared-networks-normalized.csv" | url }}">sppd-shared-networks-normalized.csv</a> (SPPD shared network)</li>
  <li><a href="{{ "/data/ice-287g/ice-287g-deduped.csv" | url }}">ice-287g-deduped.csv</a> (ICE official 287(g) list)</li>
  <li><a href="{{ "/outputs/sppd-287g-crossindex/manual_mappings.csv" | url }}">manual_mappings.csv</a> (accepted/rejected edge cases)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Step 2: Open in a spreadsheet</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Open Google Sheets or Excel</li>
  <li>Go to <strong>File → Import → Upload</strong></li>
  <li>Upload <code>crossindex_results.csv</code></li>
  <li>Separate sheets: import <code>ice-287g-deduped.csv</code> and <code>sppd-shared-networks-normalized.csv</code> into additional tabs</li>
</ol>

<h3>Step 3: Count the matches</h3>

<ol>
  <li>In <code>crossindex_results.csv</code>, count the rows (excluding header): <code>=COUNTA(A2:A)</code></li>
  <li>The result should be <strong>{{ crossindex.total }}</strong></li>
</ol>

<h3>Step 4: Spot-check a match</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Pick any row, e.g. row 2: <code>{{ crossindex.rows[1].sppd_norm_name }}</code> / <code>{{ crossindex.rows[1].ice_agency }}</code></li>
  <li>Switch to the SPPD tab, search for the normalized name</li>
  <li>Switch to the ICE tab, search for the ICE agency name</li>
  <li>Confirm both exist in their respective source lists</li>
  <li>Confirm the state codes match</li>
</ol>

<h3>Step 5: Verify against the live ICE list</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Visit <a href="https://www.ice.gov/287g-ice-gov">ice.gov/287g-ice-gov</a></li>
  <li>Download the current Excel file</li>
  <li>Search for any agency from <code>crossindex_results.csv</code> — it should appear</li>
</ol>

<p>Independent verification on 2026-05-11 confirmed all {{ crossindex.total }} entries against both in-repo data and the live ICE.gov download: <a href="https://github.com/cristoslc/data-for-press-release-2026-05-08/blob/main/outputs/sppd-287g-crossindex/VERIFICATION.md">VERIFICATION.md</a></p>

<h2>Match results</h2>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr><th>SPPD agency</th><th>ICE 287(g) agency</th><th>State</th><th>Support types</th><th>Confidence</th><th>Method</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for m in crossindex.rows %}
    <tr>
      <td>{{ m.sppd_norm_name }}</td>
      <td>{{ m.ice_agency }}</td>
