      <td>{{ m.support_types }}</td>
      <td class="{{ m.confClass }}">{{ m.confidence }}</td>
      <td>{{ m.match_method }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2>Confidence breakdown</h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>{{ crossindex.exactCount }}</strong> exact matches (confidence 1.0)</li>
  <li><strong>{{ crossindex.fuzzyCount }}</strong> fuzzy matches (Jaccard ≥ 0.75)</li>
  <li><strong>{{ crossindex.manualCount }}</strong> manual mapping (Jaccard &lt; 0.75, accepted on review)</li>
</ul>

<h2>Manual mappings</h2>

<p>One agency was added via manual review: <strong>Florida Fish &amp; Wildlife Conservation Commission</strong> (confidence 0.6). The SPPD name omits "Florida" and "Conservation," causing the automated Jaccard score to fall below the 0.75 threshold. Two other potential matches were rejected as false positives.</p>

